text: Mihály Gellér (born 5 August 1947) is a Hungarian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Hungary Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Békés County
